1
00:00:18,980 --> 00:00:24,420
♪It's a sordid story that you've made♪

2
00:00:26,700 --> 00:00:32,700
♪Up to fill my mind with doubts and pain♪

3
00:00:34,780 --> 00:00:40,220
♪Blood I shed, and tears I wept,
are you satisfied?♪

4
00:00:40,220 --> 00:00:42,540
♪Enjoying what's mine♪

5
00:00:42,540 --> 00:00:49,500
♪Have you found a way
to bury guilt and shame♪

6
00:00:50,540 --> 00:00:55,020
♪I'm coming back to life♪

7
00:00:55,020 --> 00:00:58,700
♪Through the seven gates of death♪

8
00:00:58,700 --> 00:01:02,820
♪I'm coming back survived♪

9
00:01:02,820 --> 00:01:06,580
♪Feeling great to see you fall♪

10
00:01:06,580 --> 00:01:10,820
♪I'm taking back what's mine♪

11
00:01:10,820 --> 00:01:15,340
♪Bringing horror to the battlefield♪

12
00:01:15,340 --> 00:01:19,060
♪Lay it to waste♪

13
00:01:19,060 --> 00:01:22,940
♪Til the day my kingdom is reclaimed♪

14
00:01:38,260 --> 00:01:42,540
=Her Blaze=

15
00:01:43,000 --> 00:01:45,980
=Episode 11=

16
00:01:58,540 --> 00:01:59,330
Rao Yuci,

17
00:01:59,900 --> 00:02:01,490
(Five years ago)
you are a true genius.

18
00:02:03,100 --> 00:02:04,980
You should do what you want to do.

19
00:02:08,540 --> 00:02:09,780
You can understand me?

20
00:02:12,100 --> 00:02:13,290
My parents always think

21
00:02:13,290 --> 00:02:14,570
I'm just daydreaming.

22
00:02:14,570 --> 00:02:15,850
They just want me

23
00:02:15,850 --> 00:02:17,500
to find a stable job

24
00:02:17,730 --> 00:02:19,500
and stop being so unrealistic.

25
00:02:19,540 --> 00:02:21,380
Being unrealistic
is what makes it romantic.

26
00:02:23,690 --> 00:02:24,610
You know what?

27
00:02:25,660 --> 00:02:26,450
When a person

28
00:02:26,890 --> 00:02:28,380
insists on being themselves,

29
00:02:29,610 --> 00:02:30,940
she truly glows.

30
00:02:42,170 --> 00:02:43,260
Remember this place?

31
00:02:44,450 --> 00:02:45,260
I remember.

32
00:02:47,500 --> 00:02:48,730
You were sitting right there,

33
00:02:50,100 --> 00:02:51,130
talking about Chuxia.

34
00:02:52,380 --> 00:02:54,340
(Five years ago)
Everything is ready, and we just need a push.

35
00:02:54,450 --> 00:02:55,540
Today is our

36
00:02:55,540 --> 00:02:57,220
first shareholders' meeting.

37
00:02:57,410 --> 00:02:58,220
Okay.

38
00:02:58,260 --> 00:02:59,540
So, what is the topic

39
00:02:59,540 --> 00:03:01,500
of this first shareholders' meeting?

40
00:03:01,980 --> 00:03:03,290
Our topic for today

41
00:03:03,290 --> 00:03:04,450
is to think of a name

42
00:03:04,500 --> 00:03:05,450
for our company.

43
00:03:06,100 --> 00:03:06,890
Right.

44
00:03:06,940 --> 00:03:08,010
It needs a good name

45
00:03:08,010 --> 00:03:08,980
with a good meaning.

46
00:03:10,130 --> 00:03:11,340
Let's call it Chuxia.

47
00:03:12,890 --> 00:03:13,730
It's just like now.

48
00:03:14,340 --> 00:03:16,340
In my life, Chuxia represents

49
00:03:17,690 --> 00:03:18,690
friendship

50
00:03:20,380 --> 00:03:21,260
and love.

51
00:03:22,380 --> 00:03:23,850
It's the time I feel most complete.

52
00:03:25,100 --> 00:03:27,100
It's also our best time.

53
00:03:27,850 --> 00:03:28,660
Yuci,

54
00:03:29,170 --> 00:03:30,130
don't worry.

55
00:03:30,220 --> 00:03:31,100
The three of us

56
00:03:31,100 --> 00:03:32,610
will always be by your side,

57
00:03:32,610 --> 00:03:33,660
staying with you.

58
00:03:34,850 --> 00:03:36,260
I hope our friendship lasts forever.

59
00:03:36,340 --> 00:03:37,380
For our career

60
00:03:37,380 --> 00:03:38,540
and for Chuxia, cheers!

61
00:03:38,540 --> 00:03:39,320
- Cheers!
- Cheers!

62
00:03:40,500 --> 00:03:41,340
Friendship

63
00:03:41,660 --> 00:03:42,610
and love...

64
00:03:44,450 --> 00:03:46,410
It was the most
complete time of your life.

65
00:03:47,570 --> 00:03:48,820
It was quite complete.

66
00:03:49,940 --> 00:03:50,780
Surprised?

67
00:03:50,940 --> 00:03:52,060
That I asked you out?

68
00:03:53,380 --> 00:03:54,220
Not surprised.

69
00:03:55,450 --> 00:03:59,170
Regarding that incident three years ago,
I think we were both at fault.

70
00:04:01,410 --> 00:04:02,730
Later, you did get sick,

71
00:04:02,730 --> 00:04:03,410
didn't you?

72
00:04:04,260 --> 00:04:05,610
If you insist that I

73
00:04:05,610 --> 00:04:06,820
did something wrong...

74
00:04:08,170 --> 00:04:08,920
I...

75
00:04:10,820 --> 00:04:12,540
I couldn't resist the temptation.

76
00:04:15,500 --> 00:04:17,660
I apologize to you, okay?

77
00:04:20,020 --> 00:04:21,170
In our line of work,

78
00:04:22,100 --> 00:04:23,410
there are no permanent enemies.

79
00:04:24,460 --> 00:04:25,340
You're right.

80
00:04:26,310 --> 00:04:28,250
In our line of work,
there are no permanent enemies,

81
00:04:28,250 --> 00:04:29,490
nor are there permanent friends.

82
00:04:30,490 --> 00:04:32,170
Since your girlfriend, Bai Liangliang,
is working so hard,

83
00:04:32,170 --> 00:04:33,050
shouldn't you

84
00:04:33,050 --> 00:04:34,170
work a bit harder too?

85
00:04:37,600 --> 00:04:38,700
What are you trying to say?

86
00:04:46,540 --> 00:04:47,730
Since you want to reconcile,

87
00:04:48,610 --> 00:04:49,930
I'll take it a step further.

88
00:04:50,540 --> 00:04:53,340
Let's cooperate
to take down Bai Liangliang together.

89
00:04:55,340 --> 00:04:56,170
We

90
00:04:58,340 --> 00:04:59,140
cooperate?

91
00:04:59,580 --> 00:05:02,290
Are you really that confident
that your girlfriend won't betray you?

92
00:05:03,050 --> 00:05:03,930
To the Bai family,

93
00:05:03,930 --> 00:05:05,250
a useless good-for-nothing

94
00:05:05,340 --> 00:05:06,660
and a capable daughter-in-law

95
00:05:06,660 --> 00:05:07,490
are one and the same.

96
00:05:10,930 --> 00:05:11,780
What do you mean?

97
00:05:11,850 --> 00:05:12,540
You know exactly

98
00:05:12,540 --> 00:05:13,780
what I mean.

99
00:05:13,800 --> 00:05:16,050
If your grandmother truly felt you
could achieve great things,

100
00:05:16,050 --> 00:05:17,490
she wouldn't have sent you to Lysen,

101
00:05:17,540 --> 00:05:18,490
nor would she let you

102
00:05:18,490 --> 00:05:19,540
idle away your time there,

103
00:05:19,540 --> 00:05:21,220
where even securing a legitimate position

104
00:05:21,220 --> 00:05:22,140
isn't easy.

105
00:05:22,490 --> 00:05:25,050
You're not even
a match for Bai Liangliang.

106
00:05:27,020 --> 00:05:27,810
Bai Muran,

107
00:05:28,730 --> 00:05:29,460
I'm not just

108
00:05:29,460 --> 00:05:30,730
seeking a partnership with you.

109
00:05:31,660 --> 00:05:32,370
I'm also looking

110
00:05:32,370 --> 00:05:33,580
for a way out for you.

111
00:05:36,540 --> 00:05:39,140
I suggest you
give it some serious thought.

112
00:05:40,980 --> 00:05:41,730
All these years,

113
00:05:41,730 --> 00:05:44,050
haven't you always wanted
your grandmother's recognition?

114
00:05:45,370 --> 00:05:46,540
Just like three years ago,

115
00:05:46,540 --> 00:05:48,020
when you were so eager to sell Chuxia,

116
00:05:48,020 --> 00:05:48,810
it was all to earn

117
00:05:48,810 --> 00:05:50,170
(Chuxia)
your status within the family.

118
00:05:50,170 --> 00:05:51,340
The strength of Chuxia

119
00:05:51,340 --> 00:05:53,540
lies in information
gathering and integration.

120
00:05:54,370 --> 00:05:55,490
(Content)
Not only do we possess

121
00:05:55,490 --> 00:05:57,050
advanced research systems

122
00:05:57,050 --> 00:05:58,170
and financial models,

123
00:05:58,170 --> 00:05:59,220
but in the future,

124
00:05:59,250 --> 00:06:00,290
(About Chuxia)
we also plan

125
00:06:00,290 --> 00:06:02,490
to establish professional offices
in various domestic cities

126
00:06:02,490 --> 00:06:03,610
and even abroad...

127
00:06:03,610 --> 00:06:04,250
Sorry to

128
00:06:04,250 --> 00:06:05,050
interrupt.

129
00:06:05,900 --> 00:06:06,980
We at Lysen

130
00:06:07,370 --> 00:06:08,290
do believe

131
00:06:08,610 --> 00:06:10,100
that your Chuxia model

132
00:06:10,250 --> 00:06:11,290
is very innovative.

133
00:06:12,490 --> 00:06:13,900
But as far as we know,

134
00:06:14,610 --> 00:06:16,170
your team only has four people.

135
00:06:17,050 --> 00:06:19,100
So I must point out that,
in such a short time,

136
00:06:19,850 --> 00:06:21,220
it will be difficult to reach

137
00:06:21,220 --> 00:06:23,050
your planned future goals.

138
00:06:23,220 --> 00:06:24,020
So,

139
00:06:24,610 --> 00:06:26,250
how long will it take

140
00:06:26,250 --> 00:06:27,410
to bring us actual returns?

141
00:06:28,050 --> 00:06:29,020
Why shouldn't we

142
00:06:29,140 --> 00:06:30,580
just do this ourselves?

143
00:06:31,220 --> 00:06:31,980
We...

144
00:06:31,980 --> 00:06:32,780
Because of me.

145
00:06:34,370 --> 00:06:36,020
Chuxia's greatest advantage

146
00:06:36,020 --> 00:06:37,100
is ourselves.

147
00:06:37,290 --> 00:06:38,810
Lysen has plenty of capital,

148
00:06:38,980 --> 00:06:39,810
but you won't find

149
00:06:39,810 --> 00:06:41,780
(About Chuxia)
an analyst as versatile as I am.

150
00:06:42,580 --> 00:06:43,610
I've developed

151
00:06:43,610 --> 00:06:46,490
a data research model
unlike anything currently on the market.

152
00:06:51,290 --> 00:06:52,810
Rao Yuci has developed

153
00:06:52,810 --> 00:06:55,580
a data research model
unlike anything currently on the market.

154
00:06:55,850 --> 00:06:57,660
It will absolutely make Chuxia

155
00:06:57,660 --> 00:06:58,730
stand out.

156
00:07:01,800 --> 00:07:04,340
Want to take a look at the sweet talk
between your friend and me?

157
00:07:10,050 --> 00:07:11,760
There's something
I'm very curious about.

158
00:07:12,780 --> 00:07:13,700
What is it?

159
00:07:15,460 --> 00:07:17,140
Is it simply out of jealousy?

160
00:07:22,140 --> 00:07:24,220
Toward Rao Yuci, the genius?

161
00:07:24,490 --> 00:07:26,140
Why would I be jealous of her?

162
00:07:28,460 --> 00:07:31,100
Because you can never become a genius.

163
00:07:34,340 --> 00:07:35,290
If you can't become one,

164
00:07:35,540 --> 00:07:36,490
then destroy them.

165
00:07:36,490 --> 00:07:37,700
That's your personality.

166
00:07:38,410 --> 00:07:39,100
Otherwise,

167
00:07:39,100 --> 00:07:40,220
it couldn't be like me,

168
00:07:40,220 --> 00:07:41,660
doing it purely for fun, right?

169
00:07:42,980 --> 00:07:44,460
Aren't you going to start a business?

170
00:07:45,580 --> 00:07:47,220
In terms of professional ability,

171
00:07:47,340 --> 00:07:49,220
Rao Yuci is the best candidate.

172
00:07:49,700 --> 00:07:51,930
She's a genius professionally,

173
00:07:52,050 --> 00:07:54,370
and she can provide funding
with her family background.

174
00:07:54,460 --> 00:07:56,100
She provides the talent and the money,

175
00:07:56,100 --> 00:07:57,290
and even helps you earn money.

176
00:07:57,290 --> 00:07:58,290
Aren't you happy?

177
00:08:00,170 --> 00:08:01,980
So why should I become a genius?

178
00:08:02,460 --> 00:08:04,140
It's enough just to control one.

179
00:08:12,780 --> 00:08:13,580
Rao Yuci.

180
00:08:15,170 --> 00:08:15,980
Goodnight.

181
00:08:26,020 --> 00:08:27,220
This is also one of our

182
00:08:27,220 --> 00:08:28,410
founders at Chuxia,

183
00:08:28,580 --> 00:08:30,610
my university classmate, Rao Yuci.

184
00:08:35,420 --> 00:08:36,770
We have no plans for a merger.

185
00:08:41,300 --> 00:08:42,890
You all should think it over carefully.

186
00:08:44,820 --> 00:08:45,890
I'll see you out.

187
00:08:59,700 --> 00:09:00,610
In doing this,

188
00:09:00,700 --> 00:09:02,100
have you considered our feelings?

189
00:09:02,100 --> 00:09:03,580
Who did you discuss this with?

190
00:09:03,650 --> 00:09:05,890
Our foundation isn't even solid yet,
and you want to fly?

191
00:09:06,890 --> 00:09:08,530
Moving forward blindly is just greed.

192
00:09:08,530 --> 00:09:11,010
You aren't in a hurry, but I am!

193
00:09:11,020 --> 00:09:12,960
My grandmother
and the others are all watching.

194
00:09:12,980 --> 00:09:14,370
If I don't achieve results soon,

195
00:09:14,370 --> 00:09:14,940
I won't have

196
00:09:14,940 --> 00:09:15,890
a place in my family.

197
00:09:15,890 --> 00:09:16,890
Do you understand?

198
00:09:20,290 --> 00:09:21,850
Forget it. It's useless talking to you.

199
00:09:25,650 --> 00:09:27,060
If your illness isn't cured yet,

200
00:09:27,610 --> 00:09:29,420
hurry back and continue treatment.

201
00:09:30,530 --> 00:09:31,300
Don't forget,

202
00:09:31,300 --> 00:09:31,980
Bai Liangliang

203
00:09:31,980 --> 00:09:32,820
is my girlfriend now.

204
00:09:32,820 --> 00:09:34,940
I will absolutely never work
with a lunatic.

205
00:09:41,300 --> 00:09:42,820
(A new game has begun.)

206
00:09:44,580 --> 00:09:45,370
(To investigate,)

207
00:09:45,980 --> 00:09:46,770
(I must start with)

208
00:09:46,770 --> 00:09:48,220
(your account records.)

209
00:09:49,670 --> 00:09:52,220
(Li Qiang's gambling platform
is registered in Southeast Asia.)

210
00:09:53,130 --> 00:09:55,100
(Funds are moved
through multiple accounts.)

211
00:09:56,000 --> 00:09:57,880
(The transactions
are extremely well-hidden.)

212
00:09:58,400 --> 00:10:01,370
(That's why I haven't been able to find
the final destination of the money.)

213
00:10:02,820 --> 00:10:03,820
(And Bai Muran)

214
00:10:03,820 --> 00:10:04,850
(User login. Please enter your password)

215
00:10:04,850 --> 00:10:06,940
(happened to work
in Southeast Asia for months.)

216
00:10:09,010 --> 00:10:09,850
(Could there be)

217
00:10:09,850 --> 00:10:10,940
(some connection?)

218
00:10:12,180 --> 00:10:14,300
(Username and password)

219
00:10:14,300 --> 00:10:18,420
(CONNECTION ERROR)

220
00:10:44,300 --> 00:10:49,630
(Lysen Group)

221
00:10:49,650 --> 00:10:50,530
I know, I know.

222
00:10:50,730 --> 00:10:51,730
I have it right here.

223
00:10:51,960 --> 00:10:52,820
- Hello.
- I'm delivering it to you now.

224
00:10:52,820 --> 00:10:53,840
- Please...
- I'll get it to you right away.

225
00:11:01,300 --> 00:11:02,820
Hello, may I ask...

226
00:11:09,020 --> 00:11:10,260
(Wang Meng)

227
00:11:22,490 --> 00:11:24,650
Ren Jing suddenly transferred
Wang Meng to Dept 2.

228
00:11:25,090 --> 00:11:26,130
What do you mean by this?

229
00:11:26,730 --> 00:11:28,630
Since we're collaborating,
you don't trust me?

230
00:11:32,980 --> 00:11:33,820
We are already

231
00:11:33,820 --> 00:11:35,340
on the same path now.

232
00:11:36,060 --> 00:11:37,490
Don't look at me like that.

233
00:11:38,530 --> 00:11:40,130
I didn't arrange for her to be there.

234
00:11:44,580 --> 00:11:46,770
You have never been reckless, Ms. Ren.

235
00:11:47,250 --> 00:11:48,490
What happened this time?

236
00:11:50,150 --> 00:11:52,240
When I handed the project
over to Investment Dept 2,

237
00:11:52,250 --> 00:11:53,100
you were there.

238
00:11:53,460 --> 00:11:55,130
You didn't even notify me

239
00:11:55,200 --> 00:11:56,770
before moving someone
from Investment Dept 3

240
00:11:56,770 --> 00:11:57,770
to Investment Dept 2.

241
00:11:57,980 --> 00:11:59,340
Don't you owe me an explanation?

242
00:12:00,340 --> 00:12:02,220
You are usually quite busy, Mr. Jiang.

243
00:12:03,060 --> 00:12:04,370
Transferring a low-level employee

244
00:12:04,610 --> 00:12:06,130
shouldn't need to involve you.

245
00:12:07,370 --> 00:12:08,610
Regarding all the data

246
00:12:08,610 --> 00:12:10,480
on the green building
materials company acquisition plan

247
00:12:10,490 --> 00:12:11,650
and the preliminary contracts,

248
00:12:12,010 --> 00:12:13,760
Wang Meng is the most
knowledgeable person.

249
00:12:13,850 --> 00:12:15,300
I transferred Wang Meng to Dept 2

250
00:12:15,490 --> 00:12:16,730
in hopes that this project

251
00:12:16,730 --> 00:12:18,060
could progress more smoothly.

252
00:12:18,420 --> 00:12:19,220
Besides,

253
00:12:20,490 --> 00:12:21,300
Mr. Jiang,

254
00:12:22,890 --> 00:12:24,250
there are some things I must say.

255
00:12:24,650 --> 00:12:26,790
The green building materials company
acquisition plan

256
00:12:27,180 --> 00:12:28,340
was largely due to Dept 3.

257
00:12:28,530 --> 00:12:30,100
Without Rao Yuci's discovery

258
00:12:30,300 --> 00:12:31,730
and the data investigation by Dept 3,

259
00:12:32,250 --> 00:12:34,340
this project couldn't have
developed so successfully.

260
00:12:35,100 --> 00:12:36,980
Performance reviews are about to begin.

261
00:12:37,740 --> 00:12:39,650
With someone from Dept 3
transferred to Dept 2,

262
00:12:39,900 --> 00:12:41,600
it's an automatic
reduction of one person.

263
00:12:41,610 --> 00:12:43,390
For both professional
and personal reasons,

264
00:12:45,610 --> 00:12:47,220
I want to ask you, Mr. Jiang,

265
00:12:47,490 --> 00:12:50,010
if we can cancel
the forced ranking for Dept 3.

266
00:12:52,220 --> 00:12:53,130
After all that talk,

267
00:12:54,250 --> 00:12:55,820
the last sentence was the point.

268
00:12:58,100 --> 00:12:59,600
Does the person you want to protect

269
00:13:00,980 --> 00:13:02,340
know you're protecting him?

270
00:13:09,260 --> 00:13:11,060
You need to see
the nature of the situation.

271
00:13:12,700 --> 00:13:13,940
Do the right thing.

272
00:13:15,770 --> 00:13:17,340
Don't act based on emotions.

273
00:13:19,250 --> 00:13:21,300
So you chose before

274
00:13:23,820 --> 00:13:25,890
to only do what
was beneficial to Mr. Jiang, right?

275
00:13:29,490 --> 00:13:30,610
According to you,

276
00:13:31,130 --> 00:13:32,650
Ren Jing is helping Dept 3?

277
00:13:32,940 --> 00:13:34,220
It's not Dept 3.

278
00:13:34,580 --> 00:13:35,650
It's Yu Peidong.

279
00:13:37,580 --> 00:13:39,890
Didn't you know
about their past relationship?

280
00:13:40,570 --> 00:13:42,300
I know what happened
between them before.

281
00:13:42,300 --> 00:13:44,120
When Investment Dept 1
was choosing a leader,

282
00:13:44,700 --> 00:13:46,420
Ren Jing suddenly transferred Yu Peidong

283
00:13:46,420 --> 00:13:47,460
to Dept 3.

284
00:13:47,650 --> 00:13:49,060
Because of this,

285
00:13:49,060 --> 00:13:50,790
Yu Peidong even
had a falling out with her.

286
00:13:50,850 --> 00:13:52,420
At the time, I felt

287
00:13:52,730 --> 00:13:54,730
that Ren Jing was trying
to protect Yu Peidong.

288
00:13:56,370 --> 00:13:58,300
Demoting her own boyfriend?

289
00:13:59,130 --> 00:14:00,890
How can that be considered protection?

290
00:14:01,250 --> 00:14:02,220
At Lysen,

291
00:14:02,490 --> 00:14:04,060
it is a form of protection.

292
00:14:05,060 --> 00:14:06,730
Ren Jing knows Yu Peidong,

293
00:14:06,820 --> 00:14:08,060
and she knows me.

294
00:14:08,530 --> 00:14:09,370
She knew

295
00:14:09,650 --> 00:14:10,730
that if he fought me,

296
00:14:11,220 --> 00:14:13,100
Yu Peidong would end up
in a terrible state.

297
00:14:18,250 --> 00:14:19,490
So, according to you,

298
00:14:20,340 --> 00:14:22,180
Ren Jing transferred Wang Meng to Dept 2

299
00:14:23,100 --> 00:14:24,180
to help Yu Peidong

300
00:14:24,180 --> 00:14:25,180
take back the project.

301
00:14:26,730 --> 00:14:28,530
Tina, please step out for a moment.

302
00:14:36,580 --> 00:14:37,580
Then what should we do

303
00:14:38,850 --> 00:14:39,820
with Rao Yuci?

304
00:14:47,530 --> 00:14:49,300
Stop pressuring me.

305
00:14:49,300 --> 00:14:50,010
Shusheng,

306
00:14:50,300 --> 00:14:51,420
you keep hiding like this.

307
00:14:51,420 --> 00:14:52,490
What's the point?

308
00:14:52,850 --> 00:14:54,580
When exactly are you
going to pay us back?

309
00:14:54,980 --> 00:14:56,300
Give us a specific date.

310
00:14:56,530 --> 00:14:57,850
I already told you,

311
00:14:58,010 --> 00:14:59,010
give me a moment.

312
00:14:59,010 --> 00:15:00,490
Just give me a little more time.

313
00:15:00,730 --> 00:15:02,490
I've been trying to get in touch.

314
00:15:02,940 --> 00:15:04,820
I won't let you down.

315
00:15:04,980 --> 00:15:07,300
I will definitely pay back the money
I owe you.

316
00:15:08,530 --> 00:15:09,850
You always say "just a moment."

317
00:15:09,980 --> 00:15:10,650
Look,

318
00:15:10,650 --> 00:15:12,340
how long has it been already?

319
00:15:12,580 --> 00:15:14,100
What do you want me to do now?

320
00:15:14,340 --> 00:15:15,770
Even if you drive me to my death,

321
00:15:15,940 --> 00:15:17,460
it won't help.

322
00:15:30,010 --> 00:15:30,820
Liangliang,

323
00:15:31,100 --> 00:15:32,770
(Mr. Rao)
don't ignore my calls.

324
00:15:32,770 --> 00:15:33,530
I really have

325
00:15:33,530 --> 00:15:34,490
something very important

326
00:15:34,490 --> 00:15:35,850
to discuss with you.

327
00:15:41,980 --> 00:15:42,610
Rao,

328
00:15:42,610 --> 00:15:44,220
you must give us an explanation today.

329
00:15:44,220 --> 00:15:44,980
Exactly!

330
00:15:45,100 --> 00:15:46,490
Who was the one who promised

331
00:15:46,490 --> 00:15:47,220
it was a sure win?

332
00:15:47,220 --> 00:15:48,850
We have families to feed too.

333
00:15:48,850 --> 00:15:50,420
You can't act like this.

334
00:15:50,420 --> 00:15:52,250
The contract in black and white
is still right here with me.

335
00:15:52,250 --> 00:15:54,250
If you want to back out today, no way!

336
00:15:55,340 --> 00:15:56,250
Give us an explanation!

337
00:15:56,250 --> 00:15:57,770
Everyone, please calm down first.

338
00:15:58,340 --> 00:16:00,010
Listen to me, okay?

339
00:16:01,340 --> 00:16:02,060
It's not like

340
00:16:02,060 --> 00:16:03,770
we just met today, right?

341
00:16:03,770 --> 00:16:06,320
When you were making money with me,
weren't you all very happy?

342
00:16:06,660 --> 00:16:08,850
Right now, I just can't reach
this person, that's all.

343
00:16:08,850 --> 00:16:09,730
I beg you all,

344
00:16:09,730 --> 00:16:10,650
give me some time

345
00:16:10,650 --> 00:16:11,820
to contact this person.

346
00:16:11,820 --> 00:16:12,700
Then, contact them now!

347
00:16:12,700 --> 00:16:12,980
Yeah!

348
00:16:12,980 --> 00:16:14,650
Contact them! Now!

349
00:16:15,530 --> 00:16:16,300
I have done it.

350
00:16:16,300 --> 00:16:18,130
Fine. I drank too much tea.
I need to use the restroom.

351
00:16:18,340 --> 00:16:19,010
Don't leave!

352
00:16:19,010 --> 00:16:19,830
Where are you going?

353
00:16:19,940 --> 00:16:20,850
The restroom.

354
00:16:20,850 --> 00:16:21,130
Look,

355
00:16:21,130 --> 00:16:22,340
what if you run away?

356
00:16:22,360 --> 00:16:23,300
The restroom is inside.

357
00:16:23,300 --> 00:16:24,650
Where could I possibly run?

358
00:16:24,650 --> 00:16:25,250
Come on.

359
00:16:25,250 --> 00:16:26,100
Wait,

360
00:16:26,100 --> 00:16:26,770
you...

361
00:16:26,800 --> 00:16:28,700
We definitely must get
the money back today.

362
00:16:28,700 --> 00:16:28,890
Yes.

363
00:16:28,890 --> 00:16:29,980
I'll be waiting right here.

364
00:16:29,980 --> 00:16:31,940
- Right, we'll all wait here.
- Exactly. Don't let him leave.

365
00:16:31,940 --> 00:16:32,220
Wait.

366
00:16:32,220 --> 00:16:32,980
Let's continue.

367
00:16:32,980 --> 00:16:34,780
(Bai Liangliang)

368
00:16:48,650 --> 00:16:49,460
(Bai Liangliang)
(Biao,)

369
00:16:49,460 --> 00:16:51,130
(I need a favor from you.)

370
00:16:52,060 --> 00:16:54,060
(Someone owes money and won't pay.)

371
00:16:54,490 --> 00:16:55,730
(Bring a few men)

372
00:16:55,730 --> 00:16:56,890
(to scare him a bit.)

373
00:16:57,610 --> 00:16:58,420
(Also,)

374
00:16:58,580 --> 00:16:59,300
(I'll give you)

375
00:16:59,300 --> 00:17:00,530
(his daughter's phone number.)

376
00:17:00,890 --> 00:17:02,010
(If you can't find her dad,)

377
00:17:02,100 --> 00:17:03,850
(just keep calling her.)

378
00:17:04,940 --> 00:17:06,460
(Biao)
(Fine. Transfer me 5,000.)

379
00:17:25,290 --> 00:17:26,090
Hello?

380
00:17:26,620 --> 00:17:28,010
Your dad owes so much money.

381
00:17:28,010 --> 00:17:29,290
Aren't you going to do something?

382
00:17:42,730 --> 00:17:43,490
Rao Shusheng,

383
00:17:43,490 --> 00:17:44,700
hiding won't help.

384
00:17:44,700 --> 00:17:45,900
Pay back the money now!

385
00:17:56,860 --> 00:18:00,900
(Pay back the money)

386
00:18:00,900 --> 00:18:05,500
(Rao Shusheng, pay back the money)

387
00:18:11,250 --> 00:18:12,050
Chen,

388
00:18:12,380 --> 00:18:13,330
thank you.

389
00:18:15,420 --> 00:18:16,570
For a long time now,

390
00:18:17,700 --> 00:18:19,770
you've been looking after Yuci.

391
00:18:21,180 --> 00:18:22,380
Please tell her for me,

392
00:18:23,140 --> 00:18:24,700
I have already signed a guarantee

393
00:18:24,700 --> 00:18:26,090
for these debt collectors.

394
00:18:26,730 --> 00:18:28,530
For the money Yuci's father owes,

395
00:18:28,700 --> 00:18:30,330
even if I have to sell everything I own,

396
00:18:30,660 --> 00:18:32,290
I will pay it all back.

397
00:18:32,770 --> 00:18:33,570
Mrs. Rao,

398
00:18:33,860 --> 00:18:35,180
you're being too impulsive.

399
00:18:35,200 --> 00:18:37,090
You should consult a lawyer
before signing that.

400
00:18:37,380 --> 00:18:38,570
The risk is too high.

401
00:18:39,290 --> 00:18:40,090
But

402
00:18:41,050 --> 00:18:42,980
Shusheng owes everyone so much money.

403
00:18:43,660 --> 00:18:45,090
As his wife,

404
00:18:45,140 --> 00:18:46,660
I can't run away from it.

405
00:18:47,090 --> 00:18:48,090
I must pay back

406
00:18:48,460 --> 00:18:50,010
these debts.

407
00:18:50,010 --> 00:18:57,660
(Pay back.
Rao Shusheng, pay back. Pay your debts.)

408
00:19:11,140 --> 00:19:12,180
Mrs. Rao, here.

409
00:19:12,570 --> 00:19:13,700
Please take this card.

410
00:19:13,700 --> 00:19:14,250
No, no.

411
00:19:14,250 --> 00:19:14,940
It's not much.

412
00:19:14,940 --> 00:19:15,810
No, I can't take your money.

413
00:19:15,810 --> 00:19:18,250
To help with the emergency.
It's not much money.

414
00:19:18,250 --> 00:19:19,620
I'm only providing for myself.

415
00:19:19,620 --> 00:19:20,900
It's really not much. Take it.

416
00:19:21,010 --> 00:19:22,940
No. Keep this card.

417
00:19:23,250 --> 00:19:24,570
Since Yuci was discharged,

418
00:19:24,810 --> 00:19:26,490
you have been so caring toward her.

419
00:19:26,940 --> 00:19:28,010
But I really can't

420
00:19:28,330 --> 00:19:29,700
accept this money.

421
00:19:30,050 --> 00:19:30,860
Mrs. Rao,

422
00:19:31,570 --> 00:19:32,810
please don't refuse.

423
00:19:33,530 --> 00:19:35,050
This is just a temporary fix.

424
00:19:35,490 --> 00:19:37,910
We can't let those debt collectors
keep coming to harass you.

425
00:19:38,050 --> 00:19:40,090
Otherwise, how will you and Mr. Rao
be able to live?

426
00:19:42,770 --> 00:19:44,180
Recently, I've also been receiving

427
00:19:44,180 --> 00:19:45,420
some harassment calls.

428
00:19:46,020 --> 00:19:47,940
They're all debt collectors
looking for my dad.

429
00:19:48,660 --> 00:19:50,090
I have no idea

430
00:19:50,090 --> 00:19:50,770
how they managed

431
00:19:50,770 --> 00:19:51,980
to get my phone number.

432
00:19:57,460 --> 00:19:58,250
I've arrived.

433
00:20:01,460 --> 00:20:02,810
Are you really okay?

434
00:20:05,460 --> 00:20:06,250
I'm fine.

435
00:20:07,250 --> 00:20:08,900
I'm just a little tired.

436
00:20:10,140 --> 00:20:11,220
I'll head up now.

437
00:20:13,460 --> 00:20:14,460
Don't worry.

438
00:20:15,090 --> 00:20:16,220
I'm not a child.

439
00:20:18,810 --> 00:20:19,620
I'm going.

440
00:21:30,300 --> 00:21:33,980
(Chen Mo)

441
00:21:38,860 --> 00:21:39,660
Hello?

442
00:21:39,940 --> 00:21:41,250
I knew you weren't asleep yet.

443
00:21:45,250 --> 00:21:47,660
If you don't feel like talking,
just put the phone aside.

444
00:21:49,900 --> 00:21:50,810
I'll stay with you.

445
00:21:57,860 --> 00:22:00,100
(Chen Mo)

446
00:22:00,110 --> 00:22:01,530
You can't always bottle everything up

447
00:22:01,530 --> 00:22:03,180
out of habit whenever something happens.

448
00:22:05,140 --> 00:22:06,620
Let me share a story with you.

449
00:22:08,810 --> 00:22:09,660
Once upon a time,

450
00:22:10,420 --> 00:22:11,490
there was a little boy.

451
00:22:13,010 --> 00:22:14,770
His parents were deaf-mutes.

452
00:22:16,180 --> 00:22:17,460
From the time he could remember,

453
00:22:18,010 --> 00:22:18,660
there was

454
00:22:18,660 --> 00:22:20,050
very little sound in his home.

455
00:22:21,770 --> 00:22:22,660
Gradually,

456
00:22:23,730 --> 00:22:25,090
he grew used

457
00:22:26,090 --> 00:22:27,620
to this kind of voiceless silence.

458
00:22:28,460 --> 00:22:29,180
This little boy

459
00:22:29,180 --> 00:22:30,460
thought that in this world,

460
00:22:30,810 --> 00:22:32,420
all silences were the same.

461
00:22:34,090 --> 00:22:35,220
Can you imagine it?

462
00:22:35,940 --> 00:22:36,810
Even something like

463
00:22:38,490 --> 00:22:39,570
singing the birthday song

464
00:22:40,490 --> 00:22:42,490
on a birthday is done in silence.

465
00:22:47,090 --> 00:22:47,810
This little boy

466
00:22:47,810 --> 00:22:48,940
thought that in this world,

467
00:22:49,330 --> 00:22:50,940
all silences were the same,

468
00:22:52,290 --> 00:22:53,180
because the silence

469
00:22:53,180 --> 00:22:54,730
he had at home was happy.

470
00:22:57,980 --> 00:22:59,050
But then one day,

471
00:23:01,180 --> 00:23:01,940
he experienced

472
00:23:01,940 --> 00:23:03,090
another kind of silence.

473
00:23:07,250 --> 00:23:08,220
In his home,

474
00:23:09,700 --> 00:23:10,730
he was the only one left.

475
00:23:18,090 --> 00:23:19,660
From that day on,

476
00:23:20,420 --> 00:23:22,050
he seemed to understand in an instant

477
00:23:23,460 --> 00:23:26,420
that the silence of having no family
is a heart-piercing pain.

478
00:23:27,700 --> 00:23:28,700
It was precisely

479
00:23:28,700 --> 00:23:30,140
that suffocating pain

480
00:23:33,460 --> 00:23:35,050
that almost drove him to do something

481
00:23:36,620 --> 00:23:37,940
irreversible.

482
00:23:42,460 --> 00:23:45,660
(No. 48, Building 20)

483
00:23:45,660 --> 00:23:48,020
(Chen Mo)

484
00:23:57,420 --> 00:23:58,220
Little boy,

485
00:23:58,530 --> 00:24:00,330
why didn't you bring an umbrella?

486
00:24:01,090 --> 00:24:02,180
Look, the rain is so heavy,

487
00:24:02,180 --> 00:24:03,380
and it's so dark out.

488
00:24:03,420 --> 00:24:04,570
Hurry back home.

489
00:24:08,420 --> 00:24:12,810
Her appearance snapped him
back to his senses instantly,

490
00:24:14,490 --> 00:24:15,860
pulling him back from the edge.

491
00:24:17,050 --> 00:24:18,090
Hurry back now.

492
00:24:18,420 --> 00:24:19,220
Be good.

493
00:24:31,090 --> 00:24:32,050
But that little boy

494
00:24:32,050 --> 00:24:33,660
still missed his parents very much.

495
00:24:35,420 --> 00:24:36,730
He tried hard to recall

496
00:24:39,180 --> 00:24:40,810
every memory of them.

497
00:24:42,460 --> 00:24:43,490
Later, he realized

498
00:24:46,090 --> 00:24:48,250
that what he originally thought
were silent scenes

499
00:24:49,660 --> 00:24:50,810
actually had sound.

500
00:25:01,010 --> 00:25:02,880
That was the sound
of a family being together.

501
00:25:05,660 --> 00:25:06,460
Afterward,

502
00:25:07,490 --> 00:25:08,220
this little boy

503
00:25:08,220 --> 00:25:09,490
went through many hardships.

504
00:25:10,700 --> 00:25:11,940
He also gradually realized

505
00:25:13,140 --> 00:25:14,770
that continuing to wallow in past pain

506
00:25:14,770 --> 00:25:17,050
would only make life worse and worse.

507
00:25:17,810 --> 00:25:18,700
So he started

508
00:25:19,420 --> 00:25:20,860
(Chen Mo)
studying books and knowledge

509
00:25:20,860 --> 00:25:22,660
related to psychology.

510
00:25:23,380 --> 00:25:24,500
Healing himself as a doctor,

511
00:25:25,770 --> 00:25:27,090
he gradually got better.

512
00:25:28,010 --> 00:25:28,730
He also hoped

513
00:25:28,730 --> 00:25:29,860
that through his own efforts,

514
00:25:30,290 --> 00:25:31,380
he could help heal those

515
00:25:31,380 --> 00:25:32,980
who had similar experiences.

516
00:25:35,330 --> 00:25:36,140
Rao Yuci,

517
00:25:38,250 --> 00:25:38,940
I don't want you

518
00:25:38,940 --> 00:25:40,090
to go through this again.

519
00:25:43,490 --> 00:25:44,810
I understand your pain.

520
00:25:49,530 --> 00:25:50,220
Right now,

521
00:25:50,220 --> 00:25:51,460
you are just like I was then,

522
00:25:53,940 --> 00:25:55,420
terrified of that silence.

523
00:25:57,490 --> 00:25:58,810
So I want to stay with you.

524
00:26:02,490 --> 00:26:03,810
Even if you don't want to talk,

525
00:26:05,860 --> 00:26:06,730
having someone here

526
00:26:08,140 --> 00:26:09,380
is better than that silence.

527
00:26:50,580 --> 00:26:57,140
(Chen Mo)

528
00:26:58,860 --> 00:26:59,700
Hello, Chen Mo?

529
00:27:01,980 --> 00:27:02,770
Hello?

530
00:27:06,420 --> 00:27:08,580
(Chen Mo)

531
00:27:08,580 --> 00:27:15,340
(24/7 Convenience Store)

532
00:27:39,660 --> 00:27:40,580
Hi.

533
00:27:42,810 --> 00:27:45,050
You slept here all night?

534
00:27:48,700 --> 00:27:49,730
Have some breakfast.

535
00:27:50,220 --> 00:27:51,010
Thanks.

536
00:27:51,380 --> 00:27:52,180
You're welcome.

537
00:27:53,290 --> 00:27:54,090
Have you eaten?

538
00:27:54,090 --> 00:27:55,530
I have. I've eaten.

539
00:28:20,250 --> 00:28:21,570
Where are you going later?

540
00:28:21,570 --> 00:28:22,420
I'll give you a ride.

541
00:28:24,420 --> 00:28:25,940
I want to go see Nuan.

542
00:28:26,090 --> 00:28:26,730
Let's go.

543
00:28:26,730 --> 00:28:27,420
You eat first.

544
00:28:27,420 --> 00:28:29,050
We'll go after you're done.

545
00:28:38,570 --> 00:28:39,380
Miss Meng,

546
00:28:39,900 --> 00:28:41,260
could you please sync the data

547
00:28:41,270 --> 00:28:43,620
on the acquisition plan for the green
building materials companies with me?

548
00:28:43,620 --> 00:28:44,290
Sure, right away.

549
00:28:44,290 --> 00:28:47,330
This is relevant data
for past projects from Dept 2.

550
00:28:47,330 --> 00:28:48,580
Calculate and double-check it.

551
00:28:50,120 --> 00:28:52,250
These are the market valuations
of major building materials companies.

552
00:28:52,250 --> 00:28:53,890
Please get them to me
by tomorrow morning.

553
00:28:53,900 --> 00:28:54,700
Okay.

554
00:28:55,180 --> 00:28:55,730
(Miss Meng)

555
00:28:55,730 --> 00:28:56,730
(Yuliang from Dept 2)
(Is the data synced?)

556
00:28:56,730 --> 00:28:58,570
(And the check on past data,
how's it going?)

557
00:28:58,570 --> 00:28:59,620
(Tim)
(Is the market valuation done?)

558
00:28:59,620 --> 00:29:00,050
(Johnny)
(Miss Meng,)

559
00:29:00,050 --> 00:29:01,220
(Chen Xi: Wang Meng, don't delay the progress of Dept 2.)
(is my financial report ready yet?)

560
00:29:01,220 --> 00:29:03,570
(Zhang Feng: Miss Meng said she'd give it to me today.)
(Please adapt to Dept 2's pace as soon as possible.)

561
00:29:03,570 --> 00:29:04,700
(If you can't finish it, say so earlier.
Don't let me get scolded by the boss!)

562
00:29:04,700 --> 00:29:07,700
Thanks, Miss Meng.

563
00:29:08,290 --> 00:29:09,380
So many tasks.

564
00:29:15,180 --> 00:29:15,980
Alright.

565
00:29:16,770 --> 00:29:17,700
They're all mine.

566
00:29:40,180 --> 00:29:41,530
For the baby in my belly,

567
00:29:42,420 --> 00:29:43,380
you can do it.

568
00:30:00,420 --> 00:30:01,580
(Boundary)

569
00:30:01,580 --> 00:30:05,620
(Boundary Forum)

570
00:30:13,290 --> 00:30:14,420
Using only these petty tricks

571
00:30:14,420 --> 00:30:15,290
to deal with Wang Meng

572
00:30:15,940 --> 00:30:17,290
won't hurt Rao Yuci,

573
00:30:17,290 --> 00:30:18,630
Yu Peidong, and the others at all.

574
00:30:20,490 --> 00:30:21,810
Mr. Jiang invited Dept 3

575
00:30:21,810 --> 00:30:23,380
to the Boundary Forum.

576
00:30:23,770 --> 00:30:24,730
Aren't you familiar

577
00:30:25,530 --> 00:30:26,490
with this tactic?

578
00:30:27,220 --> 00:30:28,010
What do you mean?

579
00:30:29,660 --> 00:30:31,570
Mr. Jiang understands human nature.

580
00:30:32,380 --> 00:30:33,570
He knows when

581
00:30:34,860 --> 00:30:36,010
to give what.

582
00:30:36,770 --> 00:30:38,380
On the path of upward mobility in Lysen,

583
00:30:39,010 --> 00:30:40,700
there's no such thing
as being in a group.

584
00:30:41,660 --> 00:30:43,250
When Ms. Ren rose to power before,

585
00:30:43,380 --> 00:30:44,140
didn't she also

586
00:30:44,140 --> 00:30:45,730
step on her boyfriend's shoulders?

587
00:30:46,380 --> 00:30:48,660
So if Rao Yuci wants to move up,

588
00:30:49,050 --> 00:30:50,010
Mr. Jiang

589
00:30:50,380 --> 00:30:52,090
won't allow her to have allies.

590
00:31:14,660 --> 00:31:15,860
Attention, all departments.

591
00:31:17,010 --> 00:31:18,460
I'm going to announce

592
00:31:18,460 --> 00:31:19,770
some good news now.

593
00:31:20,010 --> 00:31:22,810
The green building materials company
acquisition plan Mr. Jiang gave us

594
00:31:22,810 --> 00:31:24,140
is proceeding very smoothly.

595
00:31:24,620 --> 00:31:25,420
Next,

596
00:31:26,220 --> 00:31:27,490
we will be signing contracts

597
00:31:27,490 --> 00:31:28,570
with the major companies.

598
00:31:28,570 --> 00:31:30,050
- Good, good!
- That's great!

599
00:31:35,290 --> 00:31:36,380
You have worked hard

600
00:31:36,570 --> 00:31:37,770
during this time.

601
00:31:38,180 --> 00:31:39,770
But the person I want to thank most

602
00:31:40,530 --> 00:31:41,420
is Wang Meng,

603
00:31:41,420 --> 00:31:42,620
who just joined our department.

604
00:31:43,860 --> 00:31:44,900
If not for her

605
00:31:44,900 --> 00:31:45,980
initial data support,

606
00:31:46,220 --> 00:31:47,290
this project could not

607
00:31:47,290 --> 00:31:48,570
have gone so smoothly.

608
00:31:49,050 --> 00:31:50,330
You all might not know,

609
00:31:50,570 --> 00:31:52,860
but there is another
piece of good news in our department.

610
00:31:53,380 --> 00:31:54,620
What other good news is there?

611
00:31:54,620 --> 00:31:55,290
More good news?

612
00:31:59,330 --> 00:32:01,620
Miss Meng is pregnant.

613
00:32:03,490 --> 00:32:05,620
Miss Meng is pregnant?

614
00:32:05,900 --> 00:32:08,530
I had no idea. You couldn't even tell.

615
00:32:10,090 --> 00:32:10,900
What's the matter?

616
00:32:11,570 --> 00:32:12,860
Such wonderful news,

617
00:32:13,360 --> 00:32:14,980
and no one is going
to show some support?

618
00:32:17,750 --> 00:32:19,570
Congratulations.

619
00:32:24,420 --> 00:32:25,220
Miss Meng,

620
00:32:25,900 --> 00:32:27,490
you finally managed to get pregnant.

621
00:32:27,900 --> 00:32:29,330
Your health is what's most important.

622
00:32:30,220 --> 00:32:31,010
Don't worry.

623
00:32:32,010 --> 00:32:33,570
Since you've joined Dept 2,

624
00:32:33,940 --> 00:32:34,810
we at Dept 2

625
00:32:35,010 --> 00:32:36,570
will definitely take good care of you.

626
00:32:37,140 --> 00:32:37,940
Yuliang.

627
00:32:39,980 --> 00:32:41,290
Miss Meng is pregnant now.

628
00:32:41,330 --> 00:32:41,940
For her

629
00:32:41,940 --> 00:32:43,250
and the baby in her belly,

630
00:32:43,730 --> 00:32:44,860
from now on,

631
00:32:45,080 --> 00:32:46,330
take over all the detailed data

632
00:32:46,330 --> 00:32:47,460
regarding the green building
materials company

633
00:32:47,460 --> 00:32:48,940
acquisition plan from Miss Meng,

634
00:32:48,940 --> 00:32:50,620
as well as the contract negotiations.

635
00:32:50,620 --> 00:32:51,220
Okay.

636
00:32:51,220 --> 00:32:53,900
You will be responsible
for the subsequent contract signing.

637
00:32:53,900 --> 00:32:54,620
No problem.

638
00:32:54,900 --> 00:32:55,860
You must work hard.

639
00:32:56,140 --> 00:32:57,250
Don't let down

640
00:32:57,700 --> 00:32:58,980
the trust Miss Meng has in you.

641
00:32:59,330 --> 00:33:00,730
I will, Ms. Chen.

642
00:33:11,860 --> 00:33:12,660
Yuci.

643
00:33:14,050 --> 00:33:14,900
Drink this.

644
00:33:20,140 --> 00:33:21,050
I thought

645
00:33:22,090 --> 00:33:23,770
I had hidden it quite well,

646
00:33:24,010 --> 00:33:26,010
and that none of you knew I was pregnant.

647
00:33:26,420 --> 00:33:27,810
We've known for a long time.

648
00:33:27,900 --> 00:33:29,890
But we also knew you
didn't want to say anything.

649
00:33:30,100 --> 00:33:33,140
(Mocha Station)

650
00:33:33,140 --> 00:33:33,940
This morning,

651
00:33:34,860 --> 00:33:36,580
Chen Xi announced the news of my pregnancy

652
00:33:36,660 --> 00:33:38,330
in front of everyone in Dept 2.

653
00:33:39,940 --> 00:33:40,980
She took that opportunity

654
00:33:41,940 --> 00:33:43,700
to take away

655
00:33:44,710 --> 00:33:46,010
all the contracts and data I had

656
00:33:46,010 --> 00:33:48,300
regarding the green building
materials company acquisition.

657
00:33:48,330 --> 00:33:49,290
Such burning bridges,

658
00:33:50,490 --> 00:33:52,330
and they made it sound
so high and mighty.

659
00:33:53,980 --> 00:33:54,770
I just...

660
00:33:55,490 --> 00:33:56,620
I just feel

661
00:33:58,330 --> 00:33:59,660
so frustrated and suffocated.

662
00:34:02,380 --> 00:34:02,940
Miss Meng,

663
00:34:02,940 --> 00:34:04,620
the baby is what matters most right now.

664
00:34:06,140 --> 00:34:07,250
A baby is a gift,

665
00:34:07,770 --> 00:34:08,650
it's a good thing.

666
00:34:10,300 --> 00:34:12,340
Don't worry, I won't leave.

667
00:34:13,000 --> 00:34:14,790
The more they try
to make things hard for me,

668
00:34:14,980 --> 00:34:15,940
the more I'll stay.

669
00:34:18,170 --> 00:34:18,980
Do you still remember

670
00:34:18,980 --> 00:34:20,090
what Ms. Ren told you?

671
00:34:23,090 --> 00:34:23,900
Wang Meng,

672
00:34:24,610 --> 00:34:26,210
this is an opportunity for you.

673
00:34:27,210 --> 00:34:28,010
An opportunity?

674
00:34:28,570 --> 00:34:29,780
Because right now, only you

675
00:34:29,900 --> 00:34:30,900
have the chance to access

676
00:34:30,900 --> 00:34:32,210
every single project in Dept 2.

677
00:34:34,940 --> 00:34:36,090
Your transfer

678
00:34:36,780 --> 00:34:37,380
might look like

679
00:34:37,380 --> 00:34:40,260
Mr. Jiang's order,
but it was actually Ms. Ren's intention.

680
00:34:41,170 --> 00:34:42,650
And while your current situation

681
00:34:43,010 --> 00:34:44,210
certainly looks like

682
00:34:44,490 --> 00:34:45,900
Chen Xi is making life difficult,

683
00:34:47,050 --> 00:34:48,650
it is actually full of opportunities.

684
00:34:50,900 --> 00:34:51,690
Right now,

685
00:34:52,380 --> 00:34:53,900
you have access

686
00:34:53,900 --> 00:34:55,210
to all of Dept 2's past projects.

687
00:34:55,490 --> 00:34:56,530
If Chen Xi

688
00:34:56,780 --> 00:34:57,820
and the others in Dept 2

689
00:34:57,820 --> 00:34:58,780
ever get replaced,

690
00:34:59,600 --> 00:35:01,980
you'll be the only one who understands
every single project.

691
00:35:03,260 --> 00:35:04,050
But

692
00:35:04,780 --> 00:35:05,900
Chen Xi and Bai Liangliang

693
00:35:05,900 --> 00:35:07,300
have already joined forces.

694
00:35:07,460 --> 00:35:08,570
How is that possible?

695
00:35:08,820 --> 00:35:09,610
Miss Meng,

696
00:35:09,650 --> 00:35:11,010
carefully audit

697
00:35:11,050 --> 00:35:12,860
all of Dept 2's past projects.

698
00:35:13,130 --> 00:35:14,490
Chen Xi isn't that clean.

699
00:35:18,490 --> 00:35:19,490
Do as I say.

700
00:35:29,050 --> 00:35:30,460
(For the plan to succeed,)

701
00:35:31,170 --> 00:35:32,940
(Investment Dept 2)
(I need to find the right helper.)

702
00:35:32,940 --> 00:35:34,420
(Investment Dept 3)

703
00:35:34,420 --> 00:35:35,300
(I can never again)

704
00:35:35,300 --> 00:35:36,650
(be like I was five years ago,)

705
00:35:37,050 --> 00:35:38,340
(naively dreaming)

706
00:35:39,050 --> 00:35:40,090
(that my best friend)

707
00:35:41,260 --> 00:35:42,490
(is my ally.)

708
00:35:46,260 --> 00:35:48,900
Come on! Let's celebrate our first
one million in the bank!

709
00:35:48,900 --> 00:35:49,650
Pour the wine!

710
00:35:50,980 --> 00:35:53,380
Come on, we're making money!

711
00:35:53,860 --> 00:35:54,780
A toast to ourselves.

712
00:35:55,010 --> 00:35:55,940
Come on, cheers!

713
00:35:55,940 --> 00:35:56,650
Cheers!

714
00:35:59,940 --> 00:36:01,490
Let's discuss how to split the money.

715
00:36:03,690 --> 00:36:04,570
I think since this

716
00:36:04,570 --> 00:36:06,130
is our first bit of income,

717
00:36:06,130 --> 00:36:07,820
we should keep it as a reserve fund

718
00:36:07,820 --> 00:36:08,690
and manage it.

719
00:36:10,010 --> 00:36:10,940
That's no fun.

720
00:36:10,940 --> 00:36:12,010
Shouldn't we just blow it all?

721
00:36:12,010 --> 00:36:13,130
How can we just blow it?

722
00:36:13,130 --> 00:36:14,420
I agree with Yuci.

723
00:36:14,530 --> 00:36:15,340
Our company

724
00:36:15,340 --> 00:36:17,050
really does need this reserve fund.

725
00:36:17,260 --> 00:36:18,650
But this is only temporary,

726
00:36:18,650 --> 00:36:19,980
because I've signed several more

727
00:36:19,980 --> 00:36:21,650
business investigation contracts.

728
00:36:21,650 --> 00:36:22,690
Before long,

729
00:36:22,690 --> 00:36:23,820
the whole industry will know

730
00:36:23,820 --> 00:36:24,940
about our company.

731
00:36:25,130 --> 00:36:26,900
Fine, we'll do it your way.

732
00:36:34,300 --> 00:36:35,610
This is your boyfriend,

733
00:36:36,300 --> 00:36:37,090
Bai Muran.

734
00:36:38,610 --> 00:36:39,860
We lied to you.

735
00:36:42,090 --> 00:36:43,170
If it weren't

736
00:36:43,170 --> 00:36:44,690
to exploit that little genius of yours,

737
00:36:45,300 --> 00:36:46,940
how could he ever be interested in you?

738
00:36:50,420 --> 00:36:51,820
I have some good news for you.

739
00:36:53,340 --> 00:36:55,050
That company you led us to start,

740
00:36:56,490 --> 00:36:57,300
Chuxia,

741
00:36:57,650 --> 00:36:58,570
we successfully

742
00:36:58,570 --> 00:37:00,210
sold it to Lysen Group.

743
00:37:01,010 --> 00:37:02,380
It even got me

744
00:37:02,380 --> 00:37:04,010
the Investment Director position.

745
00:37:05,260 --> 00:37:06,420
This position

746
00:37:08,260 --> 00:37:09,900
should have belonged to you.

747
00:37:22,130 --> 00:37:25,420
(They will never deserve forgiveness.)

748
00:37:30,500 --> 00:37:34,000
=Episode 11=
(Ally)

749
00:37:34,661 --> 00:37:37,101
(All animals in this production
were treated humanely)

750
00:37:37,101 --> 00:37:43,301
♪Take a breath and swallow
the words you couldn't say♪

751
00:37:44,061 --> 00:37:47,261
♪No need to force your heart anymore♪

752
00:37:47,261 --> 00:37:51,781
♪Searching for the season
we once missed♪

753
00:37:51,781 --> 00:37:59,301
♪Leave this place,
though wounded still stay strong♪

754
00:37:59,301 --> 00:38:03,221
♪You must believe
one day the rain will fall♪

755
00:38:03,221 --> 00:38:07,261
♪And wash away the mud
that stains your soul♪

756
00:38:07,261 --> 00:38:10,781
♪Find your freedom in the wild♪

757
00:38:10,781 --> 00:38:14,741
♪Take your stride and move ahead♪

758
00:38:14,741 --> 00:38:18,901
♪I will stay behind
and wait for your eyes♪

759
00:38:18,901 --> 00:38:23,101
♪To rebuild
the same flesh and soul again♪

760
00:38:23,101 --> 00:38:26,901
♪Wander freely through the thorns♪

761
00:38:26,901 --> 00:38:30,981
♪Keep walking through the light♪

762
00:38:30,981 --> 00:38:35,181
♪Fate is absurd, don't stop for anyone♪

763
00:38:35,181 --> 00:38:41,501
♪What you dare to lose
will one day be your own♪

764
00:38:58,621 --> 00:39:05,261
♪I'm sorry, I still owe you these words♪

765
00:39:05,261 --> 00:39:09,101
♪An apology that came too late♪

766
00:39:09,101 --> 00:39:13,741
♪Yet it's also the path
that saves my soul♪

767
00:39:13,821 --> 00:39:21,221
♪When the cold wind
passes it takes the past away♪

768
00:39:21,221 --> 00:39:25,301
♪You must believe and stand unwavering♪

769
00:39:25,301 --> 00:39:29,381
♪There will be hands
to pull you from the deep♪

770
00:39:29,381 --> 00:39:33,381
♪Find your freedom in the silence♪

771
00:39:33,381 --> 00:39:37,141
♪Let your wounds be mended♪

772
00:39:37,141 --> 00:39:41,341
♪Gray is not the past
and pain is not a shame♪

773
00:39:41,341 --> 00:39:45,501
♪Sometimes the sunlight
makes the world look crueler♪

774
00:39:45,501 --> 00:39:49,221
♪Wander through the echoes of regret♪

775
00:39:49,221 --> 00:39:53,261
♪Be forgiven and be sheltered♪

776
00:39:53,261 --> 00:39:57,301
♪After everything shatters,
hold my hand♪

777
00:39:57,301 --> 00:40:03,501
♪A flower reborn
will finally bloom forever♪
